\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->

This package is part of the Simulation Validation Suite. It produces 
histograms for validating hits and clusters reconstructed in the silicon tracker.

\subsection interface Public interface
<!-- List the classes that are provided for use in other packages (if any) -->

- SiPixelRecHitsValid
- SiStripRecHitsValid

\subsection modules Modules
<!-- Describe modules implemented in this package and their parameter set -->

- SiStripRecHitsValid Strip tracker rechit validation class.
- SiPixelRecHitsValid Pixel tracker rechit validation class.

\subsection tests Unit tests and examples
<!-- Describe cppunit tests and example configuration files -->

To run the pixel rechit validation: cmsRun test/SiPixelRecHitsValid.cfg.

To run the strip rechit validation: cmsRun test/SiStripRecHitsValid.cfg.

